NAME
evolution-clamav.sh - Scan incoming mail in evolution with clamav in the
foregrond
SYNOPSIS
evolution-clamav.sh [OPTION]
DESCRIPTION
The script is designed to be a filter in evolution getting input on stdin and
using clamav in the foreground to scan for viruses.
OPTIONS
-h, --help  prints usage information.

-V, --version  prints version information
EXIT STATUS
0 - Success

1 - General failure

64 - Error in command line

